                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Anacardo <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> rectori <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs> beati Sancti Petri sita in loco
                        Castellione prope Fernetam <foreign>dona pro anima</foreign> Deo et tibi
                                <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs> beati Sancti Colombani, <rs>constructa</rs> a viro
                        beatissimo domno Peredeo in Dei nomine <rs>episcopo</rs> prope
                            <rs>murum</rs>
                                <rs>civitatis</rs> nostrae Lucensis, <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> ipsam ubi resedere
                        videor, cum <rs>omnibus rebus</rs> meis, tam quam ipsam rem quam ibidem per
                        dotem confirmavi quam et ubique mihi pertenentem <rs>terram</rs>,
                            <rs>vineam</rs>, <rs>orta</rs>, <rs>oliveta</rs>, <rs>silvas</rs>,
                            <rs>castaneum</rs>, virgarium (…), nisi scerpham meam et pannos, buttes
                        et arca vel alia usitilia casae seu <rs>nutrimina</rs>, quae in meam reservo
                        potestatem. <foreign>Ne riserva l’usufrutto vitalizio, ma non la possibilità
                            di cedere i beni, per sé et per</foreign> Auriperta presbiteria mea (…).
                            <foreign>Dopo la sua morte i beni e la chiesa appartengano</foreign> in
                        iamdicta ecclesia <foreign>(scil. di S. Colombano)</foreign> vel de
                            <rs>pontefice</rs> qui pro tempore fuerit (…). Actum Luca.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni:</foreign> (ss) Anacard <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiter</rs>; + Petti <rs>aurificis</rs> germani eius testis; +
                        Peretheuli <rs>acoliti</rs> filii quondam Gauderali testis; (ss) Firmo <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) Sprinca <rs>clericus</rs>; (ss) Emmo
                            <rs>clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: Austripertus
                            <rs>clericus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>MDL IV/1, 23; reg. MDL V/2, n. 106; CDL II, 219, pp. 252-254; ChLA,
                    XXXIV, 1001.</p>
                    </div>
